#, no-wrap
msgid "Security Testing"
msgstr "安全测试"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This document describes how to test Quarkus Security."
msgstr "本文档介绍了如何测试 Quarkus Security。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Configuring User Information"
msgstr "配置用户信息"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can use xref:security-properties.adoc[quarkus-elytron-security-properties-file] for testing security. This supports both embedding user info in `application.properties` and standalone properties files."
msgstr "您可以使用 xref:security-properties.adoc[quarkus-elytron-security-properties-file] 进行安全测试。该工具既支持将用户信息嵌入 `application.properties` 文件中，也支持独立的属性文件。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "For example, the following configuration will allow for configuring the users in both the production where OAuth2 is required and development modes using xref:config.adoc#configuration-profiles[Configuration Profiles]."
msgstr "例如，以下配置允许使用 xref:config.adoc#configuration-profiles[配置文件] 在需要使用 OAuth2 的生产模式和开发模式下配置用户。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Test Security Extension"
msgstr "测试安全扩展"

#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Quarkus provides explicit support for testing with different users, and with the security subsystem disabled. To use\n"
"this you must include the `quarkus-test-security` dependency:"
msgstr "Quarkus 明确支持使用不同用户进行测试，以及在禁用安全子系统的情况下进行测试。要使用此功能，必须引入 `quarkus-test-security` 依赖项："

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "pom.xml"
msgstr "pom.xml"

#. type: Block title
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, no-wrap
msgid "build.gradle"
msgstr "build.gradle"

#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This artifact provides the `io.quarkus.test.security.TestSecurity` annotation, that can be applied to test methods and\n"
"test classes to control the security context that the test is run with. This allows you to do two things, you can disable\n"
"authorization so tests can access secured endpoints without needing to be authenticated, and you can specify the identity\n"
"that you want the tests to run under."
msgstr "该组件提供了 `io.quarkus.test.security.TestSecurity` 注解，可将其应用于测试方法和测试类，以控制测试运行时所使用的安全上下文。 这允许您执行两项操作：您可以禁用授权，从而使测试无需经过身份验证即可访问受保护的端点；您还可以指定希望测试在哪个身份下运行。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "A test that runs with authorization disabled can just set the enabled property to false:"
msgstr "若要在禁用授权的情况下运行测试，只需将 enabled 属性设置为 false 即可："

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "This will disable all access checks, which allows the test to access secured endpoints without needing to authenticate."
msgstr "这将禁用所有访问检查，从而允许测试在无需身份验证的情况下访问受保护的端点。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "You can also use this to configure the current user that the test will run as:"
msgstr "您还可以使用此选项来配置测试将以当前用户身份运行："

#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"This will run the test with an identity with the given username and roles. Note that these can be combined, so you can\n"
"disable authorization while also providing an identity to run the test under, which can be useful if the endpoint expects an\n"
"identity to be present."
msgstr "这将使用具有指定用户名和角色的身份来运行测试。请注意，这些设置可以组合使用，因此您可以禁用授权，同时提供一个用于运行测试的身份；如果端点要求必须存在身份，此操作将非常有用。"

#. type: Plain text
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "See xref:security-openid-connect.adoc#integration-testing-security-annotation[OpenID Connect Bearer Token Integration testing], xref:security-openid-connect-web-authentication.adoc#integration-testing-security-annotation[OpenID Connect Authorization Code Flow Integration testing] and xref:security-jwt.adoc#integration-testing-security-annotation[SmallRye JWT Integration testing] for more details about testing the endpoint code which depends on the injected `JsonWebToken`."
msgstr "请参阅 xref:security-openid-connect.adoc#integration-testing-security-annotation[OpenID Connect 承载令牌集成测试] 、 xref:security-openid-connect-web-authentication.adoc#integration-testing-security-annotation[OpenID Connect 授权代码流集成测试] 和 xref:security-jwt.adoc#integration-testing-security-annotation[SmallRye JWT 集成测试] ，了解有关测试依赖于注入 `JsonWebToken` 的端点代码的更多详情。"

#. type: delimited block =
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid "The feature is only available for `@QuarkusTest` and will **not** work on a `@NativeImageTest`."
msgstr "该功能仅适用于 `@QuarkusTest` ， *不能* 在 `@NativeImageTest` 上使用。"

#. type: Title ===
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Mixing security tests"
msgstr "混合安全测试"

#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"If it becomes necessary to test security features using both `@TestSecurity` and Basic Auth (which is the fallback auth\n"
"mechanism when none is defined), then Basic Auth needs to be enabled explicitly,\n"
"for example by setting `quarkus.http.auth.basic=true` or `%test.quarkus.http.auth.basic=true`."
msgstr "如果需要同时使用 `@TestSecurity` 和 Basic Auth（当未定义任何身份验证机制时，这是备用身份验证机制）来测试安全功能，则需要显式启用 Basic Auth，例如通过设置 `quarkus.http.auth.basic=true` 或 `%test.quarkus.http.auth.basic=true` 。"

#. type: Title ==
#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy, no-wrap
msgid "Use Wiremock for Integration Testing"
msgstr "使用 Wiremock 进行集成测试"

#: _versions/2.7/guides/security-testing.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"You can also use Wiremock to mock the authorization OAuth2 and OIDC services:\n"
"See xref:security-oauth2#integration-testing.adoc[OAuth2 Integration testing], xref:security-openid-connect.adoc#integration-testing-wiremock[OpenID Connect Bearer Token Integration testing], xref:security-openid-connect-web-authentication.adoc#integration-testing-wiremock[OpenID Connect Authorization Code Flow Integration testing] and xref:security-jwt.adoc#integration-testing-wiremock[SmallRye JWT Integration testing] for more details."
msgstr "您还可以使用 Wiremock 来模拟授权 OAuth2 和 OIDC 服务：更多详情，请参阅 xref:security-oauth2.adoc#integration-testing.adoc[OAuth2 集成] 测试、 xref:security-openid-connect.adoc#integration-testing-wiremock[OpenID Connect 承载令牌] 集成测试、 xref:security-openid-connect-web-authentication.adoc#integration-testing-wiremock[OpenID Connect 授权代码流集成] 测试和 xref:security-jwt.adoc#integration-testing-wiremock[SmallRye JWT 集成] 测试。"

